articles.title: Sweden-Australia highlights: 2023 Women's World Cup's third-place game - USA TODAY
articles.description: The Swedish women extended their perfect record in World Cup third-place matches, with scoring Saturday in a clinical 2-0 win over co-host Australia.
articles.content:
Sweden defeated Australia 2-0 on Saturday in the 2023 World Cup's third-place game at Brisbane Stadium, the country's fourth bronze finish in nine editions of the tournament.
